data.description: Check out this perfect hidden gem! Located in a cozy area in North Cape Coral close enough to everything, but far enough to enjoy peace & quiet. This 3 bedroom/2 bath POOL home  is just waiting for it's new owners.  The fenced back yard features your own tropical oasis.  You will have your own pineapple plantation plus fruit trees!  Orange, nectarine, graperfruit, lemon, cherry, peach trees & more! Float in your pool that is surrounded by Clusia bushes for added privacy. Your wallet will benefit from solar panals  that were installed 1 year ago! Balance of the solar panals is approximately $40,000 and the SELLERS ARE WILLING TO PAY HALF OF THE BALANCE OWED AT CLOSING OR How About a Buyer Interest Rate Buy Down (1%) for one Year??? We Can Come Up With Some Creative Ideas. With the panals paid off, you will only have a $25/month electric bill. This home sustained no damage from Hurricane Ian other then minimal soffit and gutters. It is a great/sturdy home! It has a brand new PVC white fence, the roof is 2017, A/C is 2021.  A new pump on the well for septic was just installed, septic pumped 1 year ago, & the hot water heater is 5 years old.
